@page "/azure"

<div class="space-y-6">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-gray-800">Planned Azure Services Integration</h1>

    <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-3xl shadow-xl border border-gray-100 space-y-4">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-teal-700">Deployment and Data Services</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700">
            For production deployment, the FitTrack Pro application is designed to leverage core Azure services for hosting, data storage, and security.
        </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Azure Services Cards -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">

        <!-- Azure App Service -->
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-3xl shadow-xl border-l-4 border-blue-600 space-y-3">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-blue-700">Azure App Service</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">
                **Purpose:** Hosting the Blazor Server application (backend and UI).
            </p>
            <p class="text-gray-700">
                Provides scalable, fully managed Platform as a Service (PaaS) for hosting the .NET Web App, handling automatic scaling and deployment slots for updates.
            </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Azure SQL Database -->
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-3xl shadow-xl border-l-4 border-purple-600 space-y-3">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-purple-700">Azure SQL Database</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">
                **Purpose:** Persistent storage for user profiles and fitness logs.
            </p>
            <p class="text-gray-700">
                A highly secure and performant cloud database for storing structured fitness data (workouts, goals, measurements). Managed service reduces administrative overhead.
            </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Azure Key Vault -->
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-3xl shadow-xl border-l-4 border-yellow-600 space-y-3">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-yellow-700">Azure Key Vault (Planned)</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">
                **Purpose:** Securely storing database connection strings and API keys.
            </p>
            <p class="text-gray-700">
                Ensures that sensitive information is never checked into source control and is only accessible by the Azure App Service instance at runtime, improving security posture.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>